CPP OOP NOTES:

Why OOP?
--------

    -Faster
    -DRY code
    -maintain, modify, debug
    -short

Class vs Object
---------------

    class  |         object
    fruit  |    apple, banaba, lichi
     car   |     bmw, toyota, audi
  template |        instance

Keyword
-------

    class public MyClass myNum myString

Class Methods
-------------

    Declaration 2 way
        -from inside
        -from outside(define outside)
        
Constructors
------------

    -have no return value
    -same name as class and it is a special method which is called asap when new object is created
    
Access Specifiers
-----------------

    public private(dafault) protected
    
